PROJECT PHOENIX - WORKFLOW v1.0

1. One engineering artifact at a time.

2. ChatGPT generates one complete artifact.

3. User uploads artifact to GitHub.

4. User commits artifact.

5. User confirms commit.

6. Only after confirmation does ChatGPT generate the next artifact.

7. Overall project progress increases only after a successfully committed engineering artifact.

8. GitHub repository is the single source of truth for the project.
